  <div class="block-region-sub-hero"><div class="container">
  <div class="articleLargePhoto">
    <h1 class="text-center"> 2022 Business Leaders of the Year</h1>
    <div class="articleNewsImage">
                  <div class="mobileFullImg">
            <img src="https://www.mainebiz.biz/sites/default/files/styles/article_details_body/public/2022-03/bloy22_honorees_awardpage_970x600.jpg?itok=RDe1EkV2" class="img-responsive" alt="">
          </div>
          <span class="field--name-field-image-credit"> </span>
          <span class="field--name-field-square-image-caption"> </span>
            </div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>

  
  

  <div class="container pageWapper1">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12 borderRightAfter">
        <div class="block-region-fold-3-left">


<section class="block block-ctools-block block-entity-fieldnodefield-award-short-description clearfix">
  
    

      
                              <div class="articleShare">
        <ul>
          <li>
  <a class="nebm-icon-fb articleSocial" id="facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" target="_blank" ></a>

  <a class="socialDrawer" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" id="facebookContent" target="_blank" >
  <i>Share on Facebook</i>
  </a>
</li>
<li>
  <a class="nebm-icon-tw articleSocial" id="twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" target="_blank" ></a>

  <a class="socialDrawer" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" id="twitterContent" target="_blank" >
    <i>Share on Twitter</i>
  </a>
</li>
<li>
  <a class="nebm-icon-in articleSocial" id="linkedin" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" target="_blank" ></a>

  <a class="socialDrawer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" id="linkedinContent" target="_blank" >
    <i>Share on LinkedIn</i>
  </a>
</li>

                      <li>
              <a id='emailToFriend' href="mailto:?body=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" class="nebm-icon-email-fill articleSocial"></a>
              <a class="socialDrawer" href="mailto:?body=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mainebiz.biz%2Fevent-honorees%2F2022-business-leaders-of-the-year" id="emailToFriendContent" ><i>Share via Email</i></a>
            </li>
                  </ul>
        <div class="expandSociolIcons visible-xs pull-left">
          <a href="javascript: void(0);" class="expand"></a>
          <a href="javascript: void(0);" class="nebm-icon-close closeSocialBox"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="latestMainArticle eventInformation">
        
                <div class="field field--name-field-award-short-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item awardDescription">
                          <p>Mainebiz is happy to present the 2022 class of <strong>Business Leaders of the Year</strong>.</p>

<p>This year’s crew comes from an <strong>array of industries</strong> — housing, social services, hospitality, food production and manufacturing-retail.</p>

<p>We think you’ll find that the five Business Leaders of the Year demonstrate vision and a <strong>determination to get things done</strong>. They’re certainly torchbearers for Maine.</p>

<p>Mainebiz invites you to congratulate and thank these leaders for their contributions to <strong>our economy, our state and our daily lives</strong>. Please join us at an awards reception on Wednesday, April 6. <a href="https://www.mainebiz.biz/mainebiz-events/2022-mainebiz-business-leaders-of-the-year"><strong>Click here</strong></a> for details.</p>

        </div>
              </div>
      
  </section>
</div>
      </div>
